              <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0 0 24px;">
                <li style="padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                  <span style="color:#8547DA; margin-right:8px; font-weight:700;">‚úì</span>
